data.description: There's so much opportunity in this wonderful home in Portsmouth! With over 1,200 square feet, this home boasts three nicely sized bedrooms and a full bathroom. The detached garage allows for ample storage space! Conveniently located near shopping, dining, the interstate, and more! Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful property your own! Call today for more information and to schedule a tour!
